{"tid":292500,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple 總部招開會議探討洩密問題，但會議內容卻被外洩","createTime":"2017-06-21T12:08:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T05:40:53.000Z","uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69f8a53498bae8550fa584d424976344ca19ecc8","tid":292500,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:08:20.000Z","msg":"無論是 iPhone、iPad 還是 MacBook，只要是和 Apple 有關的產品資訊都會廣受外界的密切關注。不過近年來 Apple 產品在發表前就提前洩密的狀況越來越嚴重，因此有消息指出 Apple 為此在加州總部舉行了一個內部會議，有約 100 名員工出席，主要是在探討 Apple 防堵機密外洩的相關措施。但諷刺的是，這個為了防堵機密外洩而招開的會議內容，最後還是被內部員工洩漏給媒體了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://timg.eprice.com.tw/tw/mobile/img/2017-06/21/5026768/hat7029_1_a69f1b959f775030bae5f92269921320.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftimg.eprice.com.tw%2Ftw%2Fmobile%2Fimg%2F2017-06%2F21%2F5026768%2Fhat7029_1_a69f1b959f775030bae5f92269921320.jpg&h=c429dc6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n消息指出日前在 Apple 加州總部招開的內部會議，主題為「Stopping Leakers &ndash; Keeping Confidential at Apple」，會議由 3 位 Apple 保安部門的高層主持，當中包括全球保安總監 David Rice、國際調查總監 Lee Freedman 和全球保安團隊成員 Jenny Hubbert。會議中主要在討論防止機密外洩的重要性，以及如何防止機密外洩等，同時也為了要告誡員工，Apple 內部的調查團隊來自前國安局、聯邦調查局和軍方，內部的爆料者最後都會被 Apple 追查到。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Jenny Hubbert 在會議中表示中國的工廠和 Apple 加州的總部都是洩密的來源，而中國工廠員工相對比較低的薪水是引發他們洩密的原因。不過整體來看，Apple 去年由加州總部外洩的資料比起整個供應鏈加起來的還要多。所以 David Rice 在散會前重申，要求參予此會議的 Apple 員工無論生活和工作都要更加謹慎，嚴守保密的原則。<br />\n<br />\n不過我們能夠得知上面提及的 Apple 內部會議相關內容，全因為有參予此會議的 Apple 員工洩密，甚至將會議內容的錄音檔案提供給海外網站 The Outline。而這也印證了洩密問題在 Apple 加州總部真的相當嚴重。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.eprice.com.tw/mobile/talk/4544/5026768/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.tw%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F5026768%2F1%2F&d=f%2B4lu%2FvI2JV00Q%2FlOQOp9kkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=adb1c46e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.eprice.com.tw/mobile/talk/4544/5026768/1/</a>"},{"pid":"8f2e1b74371d211712aa34337460e351be77d62f","tid":292500,"uid":51720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:19:09.000Z","msg":"真正膠聞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94ac69ee399889f143b79f5b7af185ca103acf9","tid":292500,"uid":10905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:26:59.000Z","msg":"應該要再開個會傾下咩方法防止會議探討內容洩漏"},{"pid":"10eb9f3de9f9dbae334d14f1c517bc543bb132b4","tid":292500,"uid":20286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:30:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該要再開個會傾下咩方法防止會議探討內容洩漏</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14beabcca5dbb5a1d4a1091159b3646977ae0e8f","tid":292500,"uid":23677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:46:18.000Z","msg":"將篇文蘋果個名改做三星 一樣通用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcbee084ce426424fd0848091c8a08f6fe1858c","tid":292500,"uid":4330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:49:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>將篇文蘋果個名改做三星 一樣通用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n三星？wfc"},{"pid":"9df1608ea6d67c89e30f9713424d222a80b15574","tid":292500,"uid":52068,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T12:52:48.000Z","msg":"實捉到你"},{"pid":"b5fd298d82ece055387b795b603bdefa08de8a55","tid":292500,"uid":36964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:05:47.000Z","msg":"今次我覺得係專登流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e721000a38933d0925a80fce72786f7b6fa7531a","tid":292500,"uid":46943,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T13:08:43.000Z",